    title    = {Soundscape assessment methods: Compatibility of questionnaires and narrative interview based on ISO 12913-2 Investigating the morphological and behavioral factors in urban soundscape View project Development of medical solutions with vibro-acoustics View project Soundscape assessment methods: Compatibility of questionnaires and narrative interview based on ISO 12913-2},
